headline: Wells Fargo Expands in Louisiana, Recruits $1.7 Billion Morgan Stanley Team
summary: Wells Fargo’s Baton Rouge, La. branch also hired Nicole Fawley, a solo advisor who oversaw $100 million in client assets at Morgan Stanley.

headline: Wells Fargo & Company Declares Cash Dividends on Preferred Stock
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, August 15, 2025--Wells Fargo & Company (NYSE: WFC) today announced dividends on six series of preferred stock.
